    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-8066-bf83-f30494d90ec5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Previous research established a relationship between engagement and emotional investment of learners. Authors focus on using a model called CNN-Transformer to measure engagement from learner position and facial expressions. Model is able to predict engagement of new participants with an accuracy of 93%. ",
